## What We're Building

**Strategic Clarity** is Stage 2 of Jake Sebok's high-ticket coaching program (Aligned Power). It connects a person's daily actions directly to the outcomes they wish to see. It also runs as a live **Strategic Intensive** (same worksheets, facilitated live).

**The payoff:** All worksheets feed a Master Prompt that turns any AI (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini) into a personalized executive coach, strategic advisor, and virtual assistant that optimizes for the user's core values and never compromises them.

**VAP Coach workflow:** (1) **Generation:** User starts a chat with the master prompt; attaches completed worksheets file (preferred) or pastes below the line. AI outputs Master Context + Blueprint. (2) **Ongoing coaching:** User uses Master Context as persistent context—paste at start of conversations or add to AI project/custom instructions.

