## Confirmed Decisions

| Item | Decision |
|------|----------|
| **Order** | MIQs → WHY → Values → Becoming You → Reality Check → GTM → ONE THING → AI OS → 50 Questions |
| **Strategic Intensives** | Same worksheets, facilitated live. No separate intensive-only materials. |
| **Video style** | Jake Sebok voice (`Resources/Jake's Voice/JAKE-SEBOK-WRITING-STYLE.md`). 5–15 min each. Teaching + context + why it matters + facilitate the exercise. |
| **Worksheet format** | Google Doc. All blanks = empty tables so users can type directly. |
| **MIQ expansion** | Keep MIQ simple (3 questions). Separate Reality Check worksheet (Lesson 5) holds integration fields (Must Be True, Misalignments, Costs, Next Right Move, Resistance, Support). |
| **Source: MIQs** | Vishan Lakhiani, *The Buddha and the Badass* |

